name: Stange
description:
From Jowza Collection.

- "Baa...! Who is that!"

*To make Mr. Jowza happy, the Black Jowz went in search of the White Ships to convince them to help Mr. Jowza.


In the "Jowza" collection, inspired by the art of pop art, an attempt has been made to depict a story of the mysterious life of Mr. Jowza and a special black creature.
In this illustration, we see an imaginary world in which anything is possible!
